			div(id="actions" class="tab-pane fade in")
				.row
					.col-md-1
					.col-md-3
						h3 What do I need to do now?
					.col-md-3
					.col-md-3
					.col-md-1
				.row
					.col-md-1
					.col-md-3
						h4 Drivers of engagement
							p Colour coded list of drivers of engagement table.
							p Don't use the signal strength indicator - it's meaningless and confusing.
					.col-md-3
					.col-md-3
					.col-md-1



